{"tid":1311202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡金管局曲線叫兩大銀行趁政局動盪搶奪香港生意","createTime":"2019-07-13T05:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T05:50:11.000Z","uid":217049,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71e2206a064fe1d62c274a82a87dbe637ad570eb","tid":1311202,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"新加坡金管局向國內兩間商業銀行星展銀行及華僑銀行發出警告，要求他們不能在香港政局不穩定時制訂專門的營銷策略，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主動</span></strong></span>向港人兜售服務或吸引他們將資金投放新加坡。銀行解釋，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果客戶堅持要將資金轉移到外地，那麼</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">被動</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>的銀行便必須給予相應的協助，包括向客戶解釋事件對香港資金動態的影響和對他們資產的影響等</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-extradition-singapore/exclusive-singapore-cautions-wealth-managers-on-aggressively-courting-hk-business-idUSKCN1U70DL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-extradition-singapore%2Fexclusive-singapore-cautions-wealth-managers-on-aggressively-courting-hk-business-idUSKCN1U70DL&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=347d5a2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-extradition-singapore%2Fexclusive-singapore-cautions-wealth-managers-on-aggressively-courting-hk-business-idUSKCN1U70DL&h=fdafcca9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-extradition-singapore/exclusive-singapore-cautions-wealth-managers-on-aggressively-courting-hk-business-idUSKCN1U70DL</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n新加坡食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma